===Noun===
'''striations'''

# In [[mineralogy]], parallel [[grooves]] and [[ridges]] in a [[rock]], formed by repeated twinning of [[crystal]]s.  
# In [[geomorphology]], parallel [[scratch]] lines in rock [[outcrop]]s, formed when [[glacier]]s dragged rocks across the landscape.